<a name = "statue"><h2>STATUE</h2></a>
<h3>By <a href="brink02#statue.biog">Helen Foster</a></h3>


<pre><h4>
We must all need a statue
 smooth marble fingertips
when mothers are gone

Revise love
 with engines of destruction
  revert
 but
She in your infernal temple
 is light and darkness
 is everything
 is emptiness

Sway
 words can sway
Then you do not know in the mutiny
 what belongs

Shifting
 not fixed

Cracked by heat

arced
 
shut out


</h4></pre>
<hr>
