Kenny Knight likes to write long poems and has written many long poems. Hailed by the Plymouth Press as "Plymouth's Own", and hailed by Phil Bowen as his South West 'Tip for the Top' (whatever that means), KK is a man with long hair and lives by the Marina and Arts Centre. <br><hr>



