<a name="shaman.biog">   
     </a><hr>
Viv Grant is from the South West of England. She is a lecturer in art and
photography. She is also a <a href="http://writing.upenn.edu/epc/ezines/brink/brink01/index.html#twers">Terrible Worker</a>. Her husband has his latest album out on the Web. 
<hr>

